border-box;padding-left: 4px;font-size: 16px;margin: 0;">That God is real, =
whether you call it God, Universal Consciousness, or something else.</p></l=
i><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px;"><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55);li=
ne-height: 26px;margin-bottom: 0;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 4px;f=
ont-size: 16px;margin: 0;">That Consciousness is fundamental, and that we a=
